and I pose like this, right?

173
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:00,733
Yes, that's right.

174
00:10:06,866 --> 00:10:09,433
Okay, let's get started
if we're all ready.

175
00:10:09,433 --> 00:10:10,900
- Yes, director.
