232
00:12:50,616 --> 00:12:51,366
(Salt)

233
00:12:51,366 --> 00:12:53,000
Hey!

234
00:12:56,366 --> 00:12:58,066
You punk!

235
00:13:02,066 --> 00:13:04,200
